Name: Nickel Spot Price (US Dollars/Ton)
Periodicity:
Annual From Dec 1900 To Sep 1926
Monthly From Oct 1926 To Dec 1987
Daily From Dec 1987 To Sep 2020
Metadata:
Sources: Until 1980, data are for the INCO price, c.i.f. Far East and American ports from the Metal Bulletin in US cents per pound. From 1980 on, data are from the London Metal Exchange, melting grade, spot, c.i.f. North European Ports from 1980.

Notes: Prices before 1980 were converted using a short ton of 2000 pounds.
